content.title: Seminar A TAMC one on one
content.content: I love cellos, something magical about this instrument, especially when one can play it like this.  An instrument of the soul.   No better way to express the meaning of Christmas.  I wish the world would settle down and stop hating and killing and realize that we are all one in this vast universe. We are spinning out of control and it is like a tornado, the only way out is exploding.  It is so much easier to love one
